title: 21. Breaking Down Your Ingredient Labels Pt. 2
description:
Hi friends! In this episode we are diving into the second part of our ingredients to know - the stand outs, the controversials, and the ones we think you can skip. Keep these in mind when you are evaluating a skincare label. As always, we love to use www.paulaschoice.com and www.incidecoder.com to help navigate through those lesser known ingredients, or the ones you flat out can't even pronounce. Xo, Tess & Lo

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly

Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics

Music by LiQwYd
